{"tid":2305883,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"廚絲食@ Wagyu燒肉放題","createTime":"2020-11-30T04:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T10:36:18.000Z","uid":205222,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"32b25a09636dc86e24f533ef999bfa7b9641a2b9","tid":2305883,"uid":205222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:32:27.000Z","msg":"就黎生日，book jor間 燒肉放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n環境好好，夠寛敝，裝修好有日式feel<br />\n價錢中上<br />\n牛有幾種部位都係任叫 ，但係食到第三碟已經飽飽地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Du2RjL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Du2RjL.jpg&h=76749bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TtMHRjO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTtMHRjO.jpg&h=570225f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有豬同雞，蔬菜，炸蠔果啲小食，仲有甜品送，甜品好有驚喜，焦糖味雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唯一缺點係時間太短，食個半鐘，6:00去到啲野上得黎都6:15，7:30就起身走了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會再encore <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc801e437a7e5806f3dc5c4ea2bf74bc2e99b13d","tid":2305883,"uid":217479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:34:48.000Z","msg":"邊間"},{"pid":"e1bd1aa452d743e1d8ae301db92a42afe9281f26","tid":2305883,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"邊度 幾靚咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0803036d6554d29d6a71f7f0d5cc3748c3ed34a3","tid":2305883,"uid":529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:42:39.000Z","msg":"幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" cla