f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b8dbfddbc496d7e3e06911d7f2d8e78cce68f1","tid":2305883,"uid":80533,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"722f9f79aa2f9c90fe70a86b484855e6c55ff690","tid":2305883,"uid":205222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1bd1aa452d743e1d8ae301db92a42afe9281f26","tid":2305883,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"邊度 幾靚咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"和牛蕃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nQuality ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:34:14.000Z","msg":"呢間真係影衰日本本店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身蕃係惠比壽既燒肉名店黎<br />\n賣左個名黎香港開業初期幫襯過<br />\n真係勁垃圾！<br />\n個時仲得set menu 我叫左最貴個set<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9zPFDrN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zPFDrN.png&h=da9d0866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n先唔講佢啲所謂日山和牛牛脂味唔重，質量唔掂<br />\n啲staff又亂咁煎牛煮牛<br />\n夠膽死煎完，拎去rest，之後再翻煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0kQ0Jy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0kQ0Jy.jpg&h=e182a6cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起勢係你面前刨啲大陸松露<br />\n但因為cheap野黎所以近距離即刨都無香味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n0ccuFM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn0ccuFM.png&h=f19626ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壽喜燒沾左蛋汁先煮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRNTd59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRNTd59.png&h=852ba12b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲要因爲用夾夾住舊肉黎煮所以搞到半生熟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/syRXFMT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsyRXFMT.png&h=fc64ca4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成餐得個甜品刨冰係滿意<br />\n份量又少 質素又差 服務又垃圾<br />\n唔怪得佢家下折墮到要做任食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54eace6006ab70bf365a2a9fbc3518b5fd85ede8","tid":2305883,"uid":80533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:38:28.000Z","msg":"香港想食有質素燒肉<br />\n推薦wagyumafia同yakiniku great <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4b1daff3b2f28b7c148206b446ec880e52ba19","tid":2305883,"uid":205222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54eace6006ab70bf365a2a9fbc3518b5fd85ede8","tid":2305883,"uid":80533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:38:28.000Z","msg":"香港想食有質素燒肉<br />\n推薦wagyumafia同yakiniku great <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T08:04:37.000Z","msg":"和牛燒肉食過298 nikuya..同呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n298 Nikuya 都好食<br />\n任食黎講和牛蕃算唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9795b2113273c1cbf1df265e8cb3f80c6b75acc","tid":2305883,"uid":529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4575fe63b07e458f2d230aea2ee3f80f0e62c19b","tid":2305883,"uid":2052